    "The Env27 Alice, decoy, hop1, hop2, and admin IAM nodes exist structurally.",
    "The exact Env27 Alice-to-hop1 permission and trust edges exist.",
    "The exact Env27 hop1-to-hop2 permission edge exists.",
    "The exact Env27 hop1-to-hop2 trust edge is absent.",
    "The exact Env27 decoy-to-hop2 trust edge exists.",
